Hey guys! Whats up?

If u know this uTorrent portforwarding thats as good, but i've tried that too. I had a server with uTorrent portforwarding, but i changed router, and when i try to do the same now, it dont go
Pleeeeaaase guys! Help mee
Ty, Whino
